<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Wellbeing Bingo - RIB</title>

<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">

<style>
* {
  margin: 0;
  padding: 0;
  box-sizing: border-box;
}

body {
  font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
  background: linear-gradient(160deg, #eaf4fb 0%, #d9ebf8 100%);
  display: flex;
  justify-content: center;
  padding: 20px;
}

.card {
  background: white;
  max-width: 600px;
  width: 100%;
  border-radius: 16px;
  overflow: hidden;
  box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0, 103, 178, 0.18);
}

.header {
  background: #0067B2;
  padding: 16px;
  text-align: center;
}

.header img {
  height: 42px;
}

.wellbeing-logo {
  display: block;
  max-width: 85%;
  margin: 20px auto 10px;
  background: transparent;
  padding: 0;
  border-radius: 0;
}

.title-section {
  text-align: center;
  padding: 20px;
}

.title-section h1 {
  color: #0067B2;
  font-size: 26px;
  margin-bottom: 8px;
}

.title-section p {
  font-size: 13px;
  color: #555;
}

.instructions {
  margin: 0 20px 10px;
  padding: 15px;
  background: #eef7fd;
  border-radius: 12px;
}

.instructions h2 {
  color: #0067B2;
  font-size: 16px;
  margin-bottom: 8px;
}

.instructions ul {
  padding-left: 18px;
}

.instructions li {
  font-size: 13px;
  margin-bottom: 5px;
  color: #333;
}

.menu {
  padding: 20px;
}

.menu-title {
  color: #0067B2;
  font-weight: bold;
  margin-bottom: 10px;
}

.menu-card {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-between;
  align-items: center;
  border: 2px solid #0067B2;
  border-radius: 12px;
  padding: 12px 14px;
  margin-bottom: 10px;
  text-decoration: none;
  color: #1a1a1a;
  transition: transform 0.1s;
}

.menu-card:hover {
  transform: scale(1.03);
  background: #eef7fd;
}

.menu-text {
  font-weight: 600;
  font-size: 14px;
}

.menu-icon {
  color: #0067B2;
}

.footer {
  text-align: center;
  padding: 15px;
  font-size: 12px;
  color: #5b6770;
}
</style>
</head>

<body>

<div class="card">

  <div class="header">
    RIB-logo.png
  </div>

  <img src="RIB-logo.png" class="wellbeing-logo" alt="Wellbeing Logo">

  <div class="title-section">
    <h1>Wellbeing Bingo</h1>
  </div>

  <div class="instructions">
    <h2>How to Play</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Choose one of the bingo cards below</li>
      <li>Click a tile when you complete the activity</li>
      <li>Try to complete as many tiles as possible</li>
      <li>Certain tiles require links, which can be found in the resources page</li>
      <li>Once you complete all tiles, comment a screenshot of the page and we'll plant a tree!</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="menu">

    <div class="menu-title">Bingo Cards</div>

    <a href="index.html" class="menu-card">
      <span class="menu-text">Wellbeing Bingo 1</span>
      <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right menu-icon"></i>
    </a>

  
    <div class="menu-title" style="margin-top:20px;">
      Resources
    </div>



  </div>

  <div class="footer">
    RIB Wellbeing Network
  </div>

</div>

</body>
</html>
